---
title: Honey, Soy & Ginger Beef-Pork Meatballs with Cucumber Slaw & Ponzu Mayo Dressing
description: Revisit the classic honey-soy duo, but add a signature HelloFresh twist! We've created tender beef & pork meatballs, which we add to a vibrant and creamy slaw with an extra burst of flavour from ponzu sauce - a Japanese pantry staple with a kick of citrus. Sprinkle
over some spring onion and go for your life.
